      <akn:section eId="sec_32_503">
        <akn:num>32-503</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Medical leave requirement.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-503_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Subject to the provisions of § 32-504, any employee who becomes unable to perform the functions of the employee’s position because of a serious health condition shall be entitled to medical leave for as long as the employee is unable to perform the functions, except that the medical leave shall not exceed 16 workweeks during any 24-month period. The medical leave may be taken intermittently when medically necessary.</akn:p></akn:content>
